00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:03.666
and anti-glycation products

00:15:03.666 --> 00:15:05.533
Because among the three stages,

00:15:05.533 --> 00:15:09.133
previous stage is the cause of the next stage.

00:15:09.133 --> 00:15:11.933
the previous stage causes the next,

00:15:12.133 --> 00:15:13.433
Let’s start with Stage One —

00:15:13.433 --> 00:15:15.433
the Dullness Stage.

