00:20:21.000 --> 00:20:22.266
using them in order.

00:20:22.266 --> 00:20:23.233
Don't skip  levels.

00:20:23.233 --> 00:20:26.333
If you develop irritation at any stage,

00:20:26.333 --> 00:20:28.333
