00:20:51.666 --> 00:20:52.633
And for women,

00:20:52.633 --> 00:20:55.600
this is mostly post-menopause.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:57.400
which makes them prone to enter this stage.

00:20:57.400 --> 00:20:58.533
At this stage,

00:20:58.533 --> 00:21:01.500
