00:24:36.166 --> 00:24:38.433
I also have two daily anti-aging tips

00:24:38.433 --> 00:24:39.900
to share you.

00:24:39.933 --> 00:24:42.466
First, for those who like to sleep on their side, attention please:

00:24:42.466 --> 00:24:44.833
when you sleep on your side every day,

00:24:44.833 --> 00:24:47.900
your face is mechanically compressed.

00:24:47.900 --> 00:24:50.800
And this compression deepens your wrinkles.

00:24:50.866 --> 00:24:52.033
So for this issue,

00:24:52.033 --> 00:24:55.266
I recommend preparing a memory foam pillow,

00:24:55.266 --> 00:24:57.400
with a structured shape.

00:24:57.400 --> 00:24:58.733
For example, the one I use—

00:24:58.733 --> 00:25:00.433
it has a groove in the middle

00:25:00.433 --> 00:25:03.933
to hold and support your face.

00:25:03.933 --> 00:25:06.066
So when you sleep on your side

00:25:06.066 --> 00:25:08.266
there won’t be excessive mechanical pressure.

00:25:08.266 --> 00:25:10.300
And your wrinkles won’t deepen because of it.

00:25:10.700 --> 00:25:12.200
Second, for people like me—

00:25:12.200 --> 00:25:15.100
students and office workers who stare at screens daily,

00:25:15.233 --> 00:25:16.633
because facing the screen all day,

00:25:16.633 --> 00:25:18.333
the blue light emitted from the computer

00:25:18.333 --> 00:25:20.700
is known to damage the skin.

00:25:20.700 --> 00:25:24.133
But those screen filters sold on the market,

00:25:24.133 --> 00:25:25.800
or anti-blue-light films, don’t really work.

00:25:25.800 --> 00:25:26.666
They’re basically a waste of money.

00:25:26.700 --> 00:25:30.033
Because they can only filter some short-wavelength blue light.

00:25:30.033 --> 00:25:32.733
But for the high-energy blue light that truly harms skin,

00:25:32.733 --> 00:25:33.600
they are practically useless.

00:25:33.633 --> 00:25:35.866
So to protect skin from blue light,

00:25:35.866 --> 00:25:38.033
there's a zero-

00:25:38.100 --> 00:25:41.033
just keep your computer screen farther away from you.

00:25:41.100 --> 00:25:43.733
You can use a laptop stand,

00:25:43.733 --> 00:25:46.333
which naturally creates more distance.

00:25:46.333 --> 00:25:49.266
When the distance exceeds 30 cm,

00:25:49.266 --> 00:25:50.133
then the blue light

00:25:50.133 --> 00:25:52.900
will have much less impact on your skin.

